PN,44801
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1774275077
OL,3,CEvery household set to get #30
OL,4,Creduction in electricity bills over
OL,5,Cnext 3 years
OL,7,FA proposal to cut electricity bills by
OL,8,F#30 per year is to be brought to the
OL,9,FExecutive for approval next week.
OL,11,FThe #81 million fund over the next 3
OL,12,Fyears has been the focus of intense
OL,13,Fscrutiny over the last week.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1774275077
OL,3,CEvery household set to get #30
OL,4,Creduction in electricity bills over
OL,5,Cnext 3 years
OL,7,FDUP Leader Gavin Robinson said the
OL,8,FPrime Minister "privately indicated"
OL,9,Fto him that he was supportive of using
OL,10,Fa fund to ease electricity bills "in a
OL,11,Fmore efficient way" for Northern
OL,12,FIreland where nearly two-thirds of
OL,13,Fhouseholds are reliant on home heating
OL,14,Foil.
OL,16,FHowever, Economy Minister Caoimhe
OL,17,FArchibald said the funding must be
OL,18,Fused to reduce electricity bills,
OL,19,Fwhich has been echoed by the Treasury.
OL,26,@pD@POUpD@dO]rD@bOUsD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1774275077
OL,3,CEvery household set to get #30
OL,4,Creduction in electricity bills over
OL,5,Cnext 3 years
OL,7,FElectricity prices are predicted to
OL,8,Fincrease due to the conflict in the
OL,9,FMiddle East.
OL,11,FHowever, due to the removal of
OL,12,Fenvironmental levies in Great Britain,
OL,13,Fhelp with cost is expected in Northern
OL,14,FIreland.
OL,16,FEvery household is set to get a #30
OL,17,Freduction in their bills for each of
OL,18,Fthe next 3 years.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1774275077
OL,3,CEvery household set to get #30
OL,4,Creduction in electricity bills over
OL,5,Cnext 3 years
OL,7,FThe Department for Economy insisted
OL,8,Fthe money must be used to reduce
OL,9,Felectricity bills.
OL,11,FHowever, the Secretary of State Hilary
OL,12,FBenn suggested earlier in the week the
OL,13,F#81 million could be repurposed and
OL,14,Fused for a wider energy support scheme.
OL,16,FThe same position was shared by the
OL,17,FDUP and was reiterated on Friday
OL,18,Fmorning.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1774275077
OL,3,CEvery household set to get #30
OL,4,Creduction in electricity bills over
OL,5,Cnext 3 years
OL,7,FMr Robinson told reporters on the
OL,8,FShankill Road there is no indication
OL,9,Fthat the "burden" of higher energy
OL,10,Fprices "is going to ease in the next
OL,11,Fday or week or even month".
OL,13,FHe said his party "would like to use
OL,14,Fthis money in a more targeted way, in
OL,15,Fa more efficient way, and not solely
OL,16,Ffor electricity", and the feasibility
OL,17,Fof that "was privately indicated to me
OL,18,Fon Thursday last week by the Prime
OL,19,FMinister".
OL,26,@qD@JOUqD@QO]rD@HOUsD@ZO]uD@SOUxD@PO]yD@
OL,26,AIOU{D@IO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1774275077
OL,3,CEvery household set to get #30
OL,4,Creduction in electricity bills over
OL,5,Cnext 3 years
OL,7,F"I still think the opportunity is
OL,8,Fthere to target that support," he said.
OL,10,F"I still think the opportunity is
OL,11,Fthere to engage with the Government to
OL,12,Fensure that it is delivered to those
OL,13,Fwho need it most, and not everyone
OL,14,Fshares that position.
OL,16,F"But I do believe that where there has
OL,17,Fbeen requests to meet the Prime
OL,18,FMinister and to engage in the
OL,19,Fdiscussion about getting further
OL,20,Fresource, that is important.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@^O]rD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1774275077
OL,3,CEvery household set to get #30
OL,4,Creduction in electricity bills over
OL,5,Cnext 3 years
OL,7,F"If this continues on month after
OL,8,Fmonth, and pressure continues to grow
OL,9,Ffor families, Westminster will need to
OL,10,Freconsider again what support is
OL,11,Favailable.
OL,13,F"But what we know today, there is #98
OL,14,Fmillion for the people of Northern
OL,15,FIreland, and that should be targeted,
OL,16,Fbut it needs to be released quickly."
OL,18,FHe added: "The Secretary of State and
OL,19,FPrime Minister are with me in this.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUxD@eO]zD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1774275077
OL,3,CEvery household set to get #30
OL,4,Creduction in electricity bills over
OL,5,Cnext 3 years
OL,7,F"They are willing to have a
OL,8,Fconversation with the Executive, they
OL,9,Fare willing to hear about how best
OL,10,Fthis money could be used and targeted
OL,11,Ffor the benefit of people in their
OL,12,Fhomes.
OL,14,F"All we need now is a willing
OL,15,Fparticipant within the Economy and the
OL,16,FFinance department.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1774275077
OL,3,CEvery household set to get #30
OL,4,Creduction in electricity bills over
OL,5,Cnext 3 years
OL,7,F"We're not going to let spats get in
OL,8,Fthe way of delivering for people at
OL,9,Fhome, and that's why I think that
OL,10,Fthere's an important conversation to
OL,11,Fbe had."
OL,13,FUTV asked the Northern Ireland Office
OL,14,Fto clarify what Hilary Benn said but
OL,15,Fwere directed to the Treasury.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1774275077
OL,3,CEvery household set to get #30
OL,4,Creduction in electricity bills over
OL,5,Cnext 3 years
OL,7,FA spokesperson for the Treasury told
OL,8,FUTV: "The Chief Secretary to the
OL,9,FTreasury wrote to the Executive
OL,10,Fearlier in the week and confirmed that
OL,11,Fthe money can only be used for a
OL,12,Fcomparable electricity bills scheme...
OL,13,Fto that being delivered in Great
OL,14,FBritain."
OL,16,FEconomy Minister Caoimhe Archibald
OL,17,Fsought to reassure households that her
OL,18,Fdepartment is monitoring global oil
OL,19,Fand gas supply chains.
OL,26,@pD@FOUvD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1774275077
OL,3,CEvery household set to get #30
OL,4,Creduction in electricity bills over
OL,5,Cnext 3 years
OL,7,F"While wholesale gas prices remain
OL,8,Fwell below the peaks seen during the
OL,9,Fearly stages of the Russia-Ukraine
OL,10,Fwar, as this situation evolves it is
OL,11,Fimportant to recognise that prolonged
OL,12,Finstability will place further upward
OL,13,Fpressure on global gas prices," she
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,16,F"Should that occur, there will be a
OL,17,Fneed for additional support for
OL,18,Fhouseholds and businesses already
OL,19,Ffacing significant cost pressures.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@_O]xD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44812
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1774275077
OL,3,CEvery household set to get #30
OL,4,Creduction in electricity bills over
OL,5,Cnext 3 years
OL,7,F"I have made, and will continue to
OL,8,Fmake, that case to the British
OL,9,FGovernment.
OL,11,F"These events underline the importance
OL,12,Fof reducing our reliance on fossil
OL,13,Ffuels, and international gas markets,
OL,14,Fby increasing domestic renewable
OL,15,Fgeneration and strengthening energy
OL,16,Fsecurity."
OL,18,FA paper with the proposal is being
OL,19,Fbrought to the Executive.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUxD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/13
